sendMessages.label: xiyimo xa mpfumelelo lexi lavekaka ku rhumela rungula .
sendMessages.tooltip: 0 swi vula leswaku swirho hinkwaswo swi nga rhumela marungula, naswona loko nomboro yi ri yikulu swi vula leswaku mpfumelelo wa le henhla wa laveka .

invite.label: Level ya mpfumelelo ya laveka ku rhamba swirho leswintshwa .
invite.tooltip: Set leyi nga rhamba swirho leswintshwa ekamareni .

kick.label: Kick out the level ya mpfumelelo leyi lavekaka .
kick.tooltip: Set leyi nga hlongolaka swirho swa kamara .

ban.label: Xiyimo xa mpfumelelo lexi lavekaka eka swirho leswi sivelaka .
ban.tooltip: Set leyi nga block swirho swa kamara .

roomSettings.label: Cinca mpimo wa mpfumelelo lowu lavekaka wa swiyimiso swa kamara .
roomSettings.tooltip: Seta i mani loyi a nga cincaka swiyimiso swa kamara .

PermissionSettingsContent.description: Mpfumelelo wa xiyimo xa mpfumelelo: 0-100, nhlayo yi vula leswaku mpfumelelo wa le henhla wa laveka .

toast.error: Ku tsandzekile ku pfuxeta swiyimiso swa mpfumelelo .
